      "span_text": "In general, then, there is a need to revise and improve procedures for the maintenance of confidentiality in primary care. Although it is a commonplace in primary care that treating an individual with a disease really means treating the family, traditional limitations as regards the scope of confidentiality sometimes seem to have been pushed too far."
